text: Achyut bhai! Itni memories hain apni ki ye memoir chota pd jaye. Phir bhi kuch yaaden taaza karte hue - Wo pehli baar 3rd year ki december mai tujhse milna kya hua, 3 mahino mai hi ghulna milna hogya. Tere aur shobhit ke saath bitaye moments were the most chill moments of my journey of IITK. Wo tere liye techkriti hospi desk ki planning krna, wo glati se tujhse PR ke bacchon ko cheenna, namit ke saath partyion pr jana, C-104 mai yunhi pde rehna, hall-1 mess mai dinner krna, aur wo tere room pr seniors ke saath raat wala session, nhi bhula paunga mai. Kabhi socha na tha ki humari dosti itni gehri hogi, Jitna bhi kahunga kam hi lgega, tu aaya bhale hi late ho, lekin ab aakhir tak ka saath bna rhega. Aakhri mai, Thank you for motivating me and keep pushing me to do great in life. We will meet soon brother...
author: Sahil  Badal

text: Hi Anchal, the PR Head, thanks yaar PR ke bacchon ko bhejne ke liye. You were so kind by heart. Aur wo kabhi na bhula dene wale C104 ke chilling sessions ke liye shukriya. Best wishes for your future.
author: Sahil  Badal

text: Oye Kartik se Oye Dopa ka safar bada hi yaadgaar hai. Humare wing ka dopu aur Aruu ka janu. Wo tere saath arihant ke mze lena bada yaad aata hai. Wo tere liye tinder ki ldkiyon ka reply sochna bada yaad aata hai. Aur humari wing jitna bhi ghumi, usme tera hi to haath tha, tu hi to tha jo sbke saath tha. Wo tere saath late night canteen se lekr NH91 se Z-Square se Nepal tak ka safar yaad aata hai. Aur clg ke aakhri mahine ko mazedar bnane ke liye tahe dil se shukriya. Bas ek hi gham reh gya ki tere saath udaipur ghumna reh gya. But koi na waqt ki kami thodi hai, abhi to bahut bakchodi krni bachi hai, jald hi milenge aur phir machayenge. Best of luck for your future endeavors aur ye duaa hai meri rab se ki tujhe mile tere sapno ki raani jald se.
author: Sahil  Badal

text: Parth bhai, You were one of the chillest person, I met at IITK. Great friend to hang out with. Itni saari memories ko jo tumne yaad dilaya, usse pdhke to mujhe khushi ne rulaya. Tere wo HEC se picha chudane ke tarike bde yaad aaenge. Wo tera "koi kahe kehta rahe, mujhe to wahi krna jo maine hai thana" attitude was lit. My lecture hall buddy, you were funny. Aur wo udghosh ki trip mai jakar hawa khakr wapis aana, hmesha yaad rhega. Shukriya jo tumne humare raaz ko hmesha raaz hi rkha brother. Bhai tera wo SAE ke liye dedication aur rasam ke liye desperation nhi bhula paunga mai. Second year mai sbse jyada dukh tujhse aur arihant se juda hokr hua. Bada khalta hai ki 1st year ke baad jyada samay nhi mila saath mai bitane ko, wrna aur trip krte like Rasam ki treat. Humesha yaad rhoge tum. Best of luck for your future endeavors bro...
author: Sahil  Badal

text: Pawan bro, kya bulayen apko shayar, cricketer, rider ya provider aur bhi anek pehchan hai apki. Saath mai yaaden to summer ki hai jab A4 wing mai cricket khele phir clg ke aakhri waqt ko aur bhi mazedar bnaya with poker and bluff. Hum bhale hi apki duaon mai na aapayen lekin yaadon mai jarur bnaye rkhna, isi treh sabpr kripa bnaye rkhna, phir milenge dost, best wishes for your future...
author: Sahil  Badal

text: Bhai pehli baar dekha to tu repi nazar aaya, dusri baar mila toh rishabh ke saath canteen mai pta chala same branch se hai, phir to ye silsila 2nd year se shuru hokr aakhri din tak chala. Bhai shukriya BSBE lab ko entertaining bnane ke liye aur BSBE class ko chilling bnane ke liye. Phir aaya techkriti ka waqt jo kaise guzar gya pta hi na chala. Aakhir mai jo latke ladkhadate saath diya clg ke aakhri course pass krne ke liye uske liye dhanayawad. Tu chaapu hai bro... milte rehna, aur kafi treat pending hai kahin bhool na jana...
author: Sahil  Badal

text: Bhai Pradeep se OO Pradeepe bulane ka safar nhi bhulunga mai. Mera iklauta sathi wing se same branch ka, tu na hota to mai BSBE deadlines bhool jata. Wo tera mujhe roz class ke liye uthana aur assignment ko saath mai niptana nhi bhulunga mai. 4 saal same wing mai kab guzar gye pta hi na chala, har jageh to saath ghume hain, NH91 se Z Square mall se Ganga Ghat se Nepal tak. Wo wing mai sbke saath baith kr patte khelna nhi bhulunga mai. Aur clg ke aakhri mahine ko mazedar bnane ke liye tahe dil se shukriya. Abhi to bahut smay hai baki jaani, yun hi milke bnate rhenge kabhi na bhula dene wali yaaden.
author: Sahil  Badal

text: Bruh, thank you for always being there for me. You made BSBE hell of a lot easier. I wish you all the success!
author: Sahil  Badal

text:
Shobhit bhai, tere liye har word kam hai describe krne ke liye phir bhi try krun to you are Bakchod!, itni saari memories kaise likhun ek chote se memoir mai, phir bhi let me try - sbse pehle to bsbe lab ko interesting bnaya, phir sikhaya ki chill kaise mara jaye, phir sbse jyada to 3rd year mai time beeta, saal ke saare fest mai saath kaam kiya, lol, pehle udghosh mai to alg alg kaam kiya towards the same goal, phir antaragni mai kya security kri bhaiii, maza hi aagya, ankur ko bhi saath leliya, wo wing to wing bacchon ko ikkhata krna, phir OAT mai unke saath meeting krna, antaragni ke 4 din bakchodi pelna. Phir aaya best time during Techkriti, tere aur achyut ke saath itna maza aaya 3 mahine mai kaam krke, bacchon ka interview lene se unhe calling pr bulane tak, un bacchon ko jabardasti roke rkhne se lekr unhe gyaan batne tak, aur wo namit ke saath partiyan aur wo achyut ke room pr senior ke saath session kaise bhool skte hain... Lockdown mai to jo tera transittion hua as meme master, chumt master, multiple personality shubhita, gadar hi macha diye bhaiya aap to. 

Aaj agar IIM, aasmaan ki bulandiyon ko chuu rha hai to uska shrey sirf ek insaan ko jata hai, bakchod shobhit sachan... Pichle ek saal se tune nirantar, IIM pr memes pr memes diye hain, umeed hai aage bhi deta rhega, Lockdown mai waqt ka sahi upyog, ghante ka poorn istemaal koi tujhse seekhe. Thanks bhai sbki boring life mai entertainment lane ke liye. Isi treh kripa bnaye rkhna aur milte rehna...
author: Sahil  Badal

text:
Vipul bhai, tujhpr likhna shuru kahan se krun, dasse se krun ki dance se krun, laate rhe ho dassa, aur dance krte ho dhaasun, you are one and only chaapun. Kitna talent sametoge aur kitni opportunities lapetoge, bina limits ke aise hi upar chadhte rhoge. Kitni memories hai saath, shuruat hui thi oddysey ke dance se, phir pahuche NH91 ke terrace pe, phir machai dhoom ujjain ki party mai, aur lo aapahuche third year same wing mai. 
Ho tum itne seedhe lgte ho holy, dekhna jald kaam kroge adobe mai. Lgta hai lakeeren hai humari khaas, jo tum jaise dost hain humare paas. Aakhri mai tujhse yehi hai kehna, ki tu hmesha aise hi rehna. Apna khyal rkhna aur milte rehna.
author: Sahil  Badal
